@gateway = http://localhost:5031
@adminToken    = <paste SystemAdmin JWT here>
@salesToken    = <paste SalesManager JWT here>
@stockToken    = <paste StockManager JWT here>
@accountToken  = <paste Accountant JWT here>
@articleId     = <paste any seeded article guid>
@categoryId    = <paste any seeded category guid>
@articleCode   = ART-2026-000001

# ===========================================
# BLOCK 1 — NO TOKEN → always 401
# ===========================================

### 401 — no token
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles

### 401 — tampered token
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.tampered.signature

# ===========================================
# BLOCK 2 — SYSTEMADMIN → all 200
# ===========================================

### ✅ 200
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ 200
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ 200
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles/by-code/{{articleCode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ 200
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles/paged/by-category?categoryId={{categoryId}}&pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ 200
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles/paged/by-status?isActive=true&pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ 200
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles/paged/by-libelle?libelleFilter=écran&pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ 201
POST {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "libelle": "Admin Test Article", "prix": 99.99, "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}" }

### ✅ 200
PUT {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "libelle": "Updated by Admin", "prix": 149.99, "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}" }

### ✅ 200
PATCH {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ 200
PATCH {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ 204
DELETE {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ===========================================
# BLOCK 3 — SALESMANAGER → view only
# ===========================================

### ✅ 200 — SalesManager has ViewArticles
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{salesToken}}

### ✅ 200 — SalesManager has ViewArticles
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{salesToken}}

### ✅ 200 — SalesManager has ViewArticles
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles/paged/by-status?isActive=true&pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{salesToken}}

### ❌ 403 — SalesManager does NOT have CreateArticle
POST {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{salesToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "libelle": "Sales Test Article", "prix": 99.99, "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}" }

### ❌ 403 — SalesManager does NOT have UpdateArticle
PUT {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{salesToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "libelle": "Sales Update", "prix": 149.99, "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}" }

### ❌ 403 — SalesManager does NOT have UpdateArticle
PATCH {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{salesToken}}

### ❌ 403 — SalesManager does NOT have DeleteArticle
DELETE {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{salesToken}}

# ===========================================
# BLOCK 4 — STOCKMANAGER → view + write, no delete
# ===========================================

### ✅ 200
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{stockToken}}

### ✅ 201
POST {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{stockToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "libelle": "Stock Test Article", "prix": 199.99, "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}" }

### ✅ 200
PUT {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{stockToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "libelle": "Stock Update", "prix": 249.99, "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}" }

### ✅ 200
PATCH {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{stockToken}}

### ❌ 403 — StockManager does NOT have DeleteArticle
DELETE {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{stockToken}}

# ===========================================
# BLOCK 5 — ACCOUNTANT → no article access at all
# ===========================================

### ❌ 403 — Accountant has no ViewArticles
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{accountToken}}

### ❌ 403
POST {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{accountToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "libelle": "Account Test", "prix": 99.99, "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}" }

### ❌ 403
PUT {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accountToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "libelle": "Account Update", "prix": 99.99, "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}" }

### ❌ 403
PATCH {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{accountToken}}

### ❌ 403
DELETE {{gateway}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accountToken}}

# ===========================================
# BLOCK 6 — PRIVILEGE REVOCATION TEST
# ===========================================

### Step 1: confirm StockManager can view articles ✅
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{stockToken}}

### Step 2: revoke ViewArticles from StockManager in privilege matrix via DB or API
### Step 3: re-login to get fresh token
POST {{gateway}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
{ "login": "stock_erp1234", "password": "Stock@1234" }

### Step 4: use new token → should now be ❌ 403
GET {{gateway}}/api/articles
Authorization: Bearer <new stock token here>